# === strongs: standalone dataset, generated + PUBLISHED externally ===
# (Hugging Face / data repo bcv-data/strongs). NOT consumed by the services, so
# not shipped in the image and re-derivable via scripts/build_strongs_words*.py.
# Keep only the authored card + license under version control; data stays out.
resources/strongs/**
!resources/strongs/README.md
!resources/strongs/LICENSE

